### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Información de la API
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ===== GESTIÓN DE PERSONAS =====

### 1. Crear Persona
POST {{apiUrl}}/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document_type": "CC",
  "document_number": "99999999",
  "full_name": "Ana María López García",
  "gender": "F",
  "photo_url": "https://via.placeholder.com/150/28a745/ffffff?text=AM",
  "birth_date": "1990-05-15",
  "notes": "Nueva persona de prueba",
  "alias": "Ana",
  "is_active": true,
  "username": "ana.lopez",
  "password": "password123",
  "language": "es",
  "timezone": "America/Bogota",
  "emails": [
    {
      "email": "ana.lopez@email.com"
    }
  ],
  "phones": [
    {
      "phone": "+57 300 999 8888"
    }
  ],
  "images": [
    {
      "image_url": "https://via.placeholder.com/300x400/28a745/ffffff?text=Ana+Photo"
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Listar Personas
GET {{apiUrl}}/persons?page=1&limit=5

### 3. Listar Personas con Filtros
GET {{apiUrl}}/persons?search=Juan&status=active&sort=full_name&order=asc

### 4. Obtener Persona por ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/persons/1

### 5. Actualizar Persona Parcialmente
PUT {{apiUrl}}/persons/1/partial
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Juan Carlos Pérez González Actualizado",
  "notes": "Notas actualizadas desde API"
}

### 6. Autocompletado
GET {{apiUrl}}/persons/search/autocomplete?q=Juan&limit=5

### 7. Estadísticas
GET {{apiUrl}}/persons/stats/overview

### 8. Verificar Duplicados
GET {{apiUrl}}/persons/duplicates/check?document_number=12345678

### 9. Validar Datos
POST {{apiUrl}}/persons/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document_type": "CC",
  "document_number": "11111111",
  "full_name": "Pedro José Silva",
  "gender": "M"
}

### 10. Eliminar Persona (Soft Delete)
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/persons/1

### 11. Restaurar Persona
POST {{apiUrl}}/persons/1/restore

### ===== PRUEBAS DE ERROR =====

### Persona no encontrada
GET {{apiUrl}}/persons/999

